These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, lacrosse
2 different games are played: scrabble, poker
2 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla
City: prague, hamburg
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, august
House: wooden, modern
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the right of the person traveling to prague##8
3. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
4. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
5. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
6. the modern house is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the person playing scrabble is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Sport      | lacrosse   | snowboarding      |
| Game          | poker | scrabble   |
| Pet         | chinchilla    | horse |
| City           | prague     | hamburg    |
| Birthday   | august    | september       |
| House   | wooden    | modern        |
| Transport     | roller     | tram        |

